          Projects / Endless Runner
        </p>

        <!-- Badges -->
        <div class="hero-enter flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6" style="--delay: 0.15s">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 border border-cyan-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
            Completed
          </span>
